column5: #Maintain the facial features, A girl is wearing a neat police uniform and sporting a badge. She is smiling with a friendly and confident demeanor. The background is blurred, featuring a cartoon logo.#

#By referencing the mask, restore a partial image from the doodle {image} that aligns with the textual explanation: "1 white old owl".#
#The item is put on the ground.#
#The logo is printed on the headphones.#
